      <h1 data-content-field="title" class="entry-title p-name">
      
        <a href="/hurstpierpoint-blog/2022/11/18/hurst-high-street-welcomes-santas-fun-sunday-back-for-2022" class="u-url" rel="bookmark">Hurst High Street welcomes Santa’s Fun Sunday back for 2022 </a>
      
      </h1>
      <div class="meta-below-title">
        
        <div class="entry-byline">
          <span class="entry-author"><a href="/hurstpierpoint-blog?author=5eff29cae4f55b6f0a18c700" class="p-author author entry-byline-link" rel="author">Kirsty Warren</a></span>
